<plot>Harry is a disgruntled bus driver, taking a group of pensioners to the beach for the day, June is old, a lonely soul, and she plans to make this her last journey. They observe each other and connect with a deep sadness within. At the beach Harry stops June from drowning, confronting his pain in the process and letting go, June accepts her fate, finding peace.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?567638</url></doc>
